I89. Election of trustee

I11(a) A creditor may vote for a candidate for trustee only if such creditor_

I12(1) holds an allowable, undisputed, fixed, liquidated, unsecured claim of a kind entitled to distribution under section 726(a)(2), 726(a)(3), 726(a)(4), 752(a), 766(h), or 766(i) of this title;

